REMOVE GREEN BG MAR15
Removes the bg from shots taken for the mar15 film.

How to use:
	Put a config.json file to the repo root
		1. Copy one from the configs dir, rename and edit it
			- config1.json: use for grey bg
			- config2.json: use for green bg
		2. Write one yourself
	$ cd scripts
	$ ./build.sh
	$ ./run.sh

How to build:
	Debian GNU/Linux:
		$ sudo apt update
		$ sudo apt upgrade
		$ sudo apt install g++ make libopencv-dev libcjson-dev
		Clone the repo
		$ cd remove_green_bg_mar15/scripts
		$ ./rebuild.sh
